{
  "stem": "17001.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cheese or sex, which one you want?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Magda Klein.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "M-A-G-D-A K-L-E-I-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The birth, my name was Magda Czigler, M-A-G-D-A C-Z-I-G-L-E-R.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born October the 2nd, 1927, in Mandok, Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mandok, M-A-N-D-O-K, Hungary, H-U-N-G-A-R-Y.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm 68 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were seven children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had my older brother and my younger brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest of us were girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were a religious family, I would say Orthodox family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As young girls, we weren't allowed to read Hungarian books.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to read only Hebrew books.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were having a normal life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother name was Ilona Czigler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father name was Ferenc Czigler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father had a big grocery store when the economy was good and the situation was good.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, they took the permit away from us and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] being that we were seven children, so the shoes had to be fixed and we had to have something to walk on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he used to go to the shoemaker, sit there, because he had all the time, and watch how they were working on the shoes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He learned the trade by watching them and he was making the shoes for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Beside that, he was making shoes for some other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were times when it was difficult to obtain the material, like the leather and the nails and all that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, some of the leathers were given on-- on ration, on ticket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you had to purchase the ticket from somebody in order to have a pair of shoes and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I mean, it was a lot of difficulties to obtain material, leather, for a pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
